    "course_title": "CLIMATE CHANGE, HUMAN RIGHTS, AND THE ENVIRONMENT",
    "description": "Examines the link between climate change and human rights, the pros and cons of using a human rights approach and the specific challenges that climate change poses to the international legal system such as the disappearance of states, displacement and mass movement of people, and adjudication. Discuss the plight of vulnerable populations especially, indigenous peoples, women, and climate \"refugees\" within a human rights framework.",
